===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-sibilant|scrat|ch|}}

# To [[rub]] a surface with a sharp object, especially by a living creature to remove [[itch]]ing with [[nail]]s, [[claw]]s, et fuck

===Noun===
'''scratch''', ''plural'': '''scratches'''

#(countable) A [[disruption]] on a [[surface]] made by [[scratch]]ing
#:''I can’t believe there is a '''scratch''' in the paint already.''
#(countable) a shallow [[cut]] in the [[skin]]
#:''Her skin was covered with tiny '''scratches'''
#{{slang}} [[money]]
#:''I need a little scratch''

